These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, pop, gospel
1. the fan of gospel is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | pop | gospel |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, mouse, bird
1. the owner of the mouse is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Pet   | rabbit | bird | mouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike, boat
1. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Transport   | quad-bike | motorbike | boat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, baking, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | baking | woodworking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-5::.
