.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-6::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, comedy, scientific
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | family | comedy | scientific |

