.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-13::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, reading, puzzles
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is camping##2
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3     |
| Hobby   | reading | puzzles | camping |

